Description: Time and weather announcement scripts for Asterisk
 Scripts to announce time and weather conditions through Asterisk.
 Uses free Open-Meteo API for worldwide weather data with automatic
 timezone detection. No API keys required! Works with any postal code
 globally. Time announcements support both 12 and 24-hour formats.
 .
 Features include:
  * Time announcements in 12/24 hour format with location-aware timezone
  * Worldwide weather support via Open-Meteo API (free, no API key)
  * Automatic geocoding via Nominatim/OpenStreetMap (free)
  * Support for postal codes worldwide (US, Canada, Europe, etc.)
  * Automatic timezone detection matching weather location
  * Configurable caching system for fast repeated lookups
  * Comprehensive logging (quiet by default, verbose with -v)
  * Custom sound directory support for audio files
  * Zero configuration required - works out of the box!
  * Simplified from 1363 to 1044 lines of code (23% reduction) 
